{"id": "1193609934714187817", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且对方图鲁整场没打多少伤害，感觉玩得有点偏盾击流，为了嘲讽叠盾击洗了几次牌，对方少用点盾给图鲁攒点牌我可能早就没了", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:39:44.636000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:40:09.077000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193618127125233715", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@655338276554801152>陨日的效果就是让卡面数值+3。翻倍和触发不受陨日影响", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:12:17.859000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193618998324113539", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "1回合的情况：拉蒙娜开大有两张群体毒，陨日效果=这是8+8毒。翻倍后是32。触发一次，再打32，共计64。这种情况下，前排吃了攻击，后排如果有个人吃了单体毒，就很容易死，也就是双杀。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:15:45.569000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193619229405102270", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "这是6费+两个大招完全可以打出来的效果。并不奇怪。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:16:40.663000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193619536163913822", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "活性的作用是阻止毒妈提前上毒，在其翻倍和触发前就净化掉。如果铺毒+翻倍+触发是同一回合的操作，那么活性是没用的。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:17:53.800000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193620093473665066", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "盾流点杀的成本比点名要高。而且运营很困难。一般来讲是要杀对面输出的，但是朵儿的净化太强了，不得已先杀朵儿。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:20:06.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["712663356032680007"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193534005866397736", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193620224172359823", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "对捏", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:20:37.834000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193620806631174174", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "但对方首次盾击没杀死我单c，后续的盾击也没能秒杀朵尔，伤害有点分散了", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:22:56.703000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193620889800016063", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "感觉那场运气占比很多，对方不太熟悉", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:23:16.532000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
